reviews.review: The hospital blends modern facilities with a calm and friendly environment. Doctors here take time to clarify each step of the treatment process, making patients feel comfortable and confident. My mother's surgery went smoothly, and the recovery care was exceptional.

Orthopedic wing is well organized and equipped with advanced machines. The only drawback is the parking space, which can get congested during visiting hours. Nevertheless, overall service quality is impressive.
Experienced cardiology team and a very responsive nursing staff. They followed strict hygiene protocols which made me feel assured. Quick insurance claim settlement was another plus point.

NIMHANS offers specialized neurological care with state-of-the-art facilities. The doctors are experts and their approach is empathetic. My treatment journey was smooth with clear communication at all stages.
The hospital has excellent infrastructure and nursing care, though parking can be a bit challenging. The mental health care wing is very supportive and effective.
I highly recommend NIMHANS for neurological disorders. Their diagnostics are thorough and the follow-up system is well maintained. Staff were courteous and attentive throughout my visits.

reviews.review: Pediatricians here are wonderful and support staff very attentive. The pharmacy is well stocked and conveniently located near the entrance.
My wife's  surgery went smoothly. Everything from admission to discharge was professionally handled. The insurance team guided us through paperwork.
Great  hospital with experienced medical staff. Emergency services are efficient; minor delays at the front desk during peak hours.

reviews.review: The hospital provides excellent neurosurgery care with a dedicated team. Facilities are modern and the staff always attentive. Waiting times can be improved, but overall good experience.
While medical care is competent, infrastructure could be enhanced. The billing process is a bit slow but the doctors are very professional and kind.
Emergency care is prompt and efficient. Doctors provided clear guidance throughout the treatment. Would recommend for neurological and trauma care.
Less Facilities for Patient to check his health

Hospital_name: KLE's Dr. Prabhakar Kore Hospital & Medical Research Centre

reviews.review: Excellent multi-specialty care with highly qualified doctors. The hospital is well-equipped and maintains high hygiene standards. Staff are professional and caring, making the experience pleasant.
Well-managed hospital with good outpatient services. Some delays during peak hours but overall a reliable hospital for various treatments.
Caring and experienced staff, wide range of specialties. The facility could improve parking availability but offers good comprehensive care.

Apollo Hospitals provided exceptional cardiac care with highly skilled doctors and cutting-edge technology. The staff was compassionate and attentive throughout my treatment. The facilities were clean and well-maintained, making my stay comfortable. I am very satisfied with the overall care.

The cardiology department is very professional and thorough. My procedure was successful, and the follow-up care was well organized. The only downside was a slightly longer waiting time for appointments, but the quality of care outweighed this.

This hospital excels in heart treatments and patient care. The nurses are attentive, and the environment is calm and reassuring. The insurance claims process was hassle-free, which eased my mind during recovery.

Dr. Mehta's Hospital me with world-class neurological care. The doctors were very knowledgeable, and their explanations helped me understand my condition well. The hospital is well equipped and the nursing staff was very caring.

The neurology department is excellent with state-of-the-art facilities. I faced minimal waiting times, and all my questions were addressed thoroughly. A good option for specialized neurological treatment.

This hospital provided compassionate neurological care during my treatment. The ICU and monitoring facilities were impressive, and the environment felt very patient-friendly. I recommend it for anyone needing expert care.

Fortis Malar Hospital offers excellent pediatric care with experienced doctors and friendly staff. The child care facilities are top-notch and very comforting. My child’s treatment was smooth, and the follow-up was very thorough.
I appreciate the child-friendly approach of Fortis Malar. The hospital is clean and well maintained. Appointment scheduling is efficient and the nursing staff attentive and caring.
The hospital provides quality pediatric services with well-equipped NICU and PICU facilities. While the main hospital gets busy, the staff handled emergencies promptly and professionally.

C.S.I. Kalyani Hospital provides excellent gynecological care with experienced specialists. The staff is supportive, and the facilities are clean and well equipped. My prenatal care was thorough, and I felt well informed throughout.

The hospital catered well to my wife’s needs during pregnancy. The doctors explained all procedures clearly and the nursing staff were attentive. Slightly long wait times, but the care quality made up for it.

Good overall experience with gynecology and maternity care. Staff were respectful and the hospital ambiance was warm and welcoming. Minor delays in discharge process were noted but did not affect my overall satisfaction.

location: A-791, Bandra Reclamation, Bandra West, Mumbai

reviews.review: Lilavati Hospital offers excellent emergency services with compassionate staff. The facilities are well maintained, and patient support is prompt. I appreciated the detailed explanations given by doctors, which helped ease my anxiety.
The hospital has strong cardiology and neurology departments. While wait times can be long, the quality of care provided was worth it. Staff are courteous and professional throughout my visits.

Good hospital with modern infrastructure and experienced doctors. The billing process was smooth, and insurance coordination was efficient. Overall a positive experience with room for improvement in outpatient wait times.

reviews.review: Tata Memorial Hospital provides excellent cancer treatment with experienced oncologists. The staff was supportive, and facilities were well maintained. Slight delays in outpatient services but overall a satisfactory experience.
Highly specialized cancer care center with cutting-edge technology. Doctors explained the diagnosis and treatment well. Nursing staff were compassionate throughout my treatment.

reviews.review: Fortis Hospital offers advanced cardiology care with experienced specialists. The facilities are modern, and the staff is professional. Slight delays during peak hours but overall service is commendable.
Good hospital with a focus on heart surgeries and care. Insurance processing was smooth. Parking and wait times could be improved for a better patient experience.

reviews.review: Breach Candy Hospital has excellent orthopedic surgeons and facilities. The staff is friendly and the environment is clean and comfortable. Some delays were experienced, but care standards are high.
Good hospital with competent orthopedic care. The scheduling of appointments was sometimes inconvenient but overall treatment was effective and staff cooperative.

reviews.review: This hospital provided excellent care during my stay. The nurses were attentive and kind, always checking in on me. The doctors were knowledgeable and took time to explain my treatment plan. However, the waiting times in the ER were quite long.

The children’s ward was clean and well-equipped. The staff was amazing with my child, making them feel comfortable. The doctors were patient and answered all my questions. The only downside was the limited parking space.

reviews.review: The ER team acted quickly when I arrived with severe pain. The nurses were compassionate and kept me informed. However, the waiting area was overcrowded, which was stressful. Overall, I received good treatment once admitted.

The cardiac unit has highly skilled specialists. They performed my surgery successfully with minimal complications. The follow-up care was detailed and reassuring. However, the billing process was confusing and delayed.

reviews.review: After my knee surgery, the rehab team was fantastic. The physical therapists were encouraging and knowledgeable. The facilities were modern and well-maintained. My only complaint was the slow admission process

As a teaching hospital, the care was thorough but sometimes slow. Residents were attentive but often needed attending approval. The facilities were top-notch, and research-based treatments were offered. Communication between teams could improve.

The mental health professionals here were compassionate. Group therapy sessions were well-structured and helpful. The environment was safe and calming. However, visiting hours were too restrictive for family support.

The rehab staff was dedicated to patient recovery. My physical therapist customized exercises for my needs. The facility was clean and had good equipment. The only downside was the high cost of extended stays.

The VA hospital provided solid care for my service-related condition. The doctors were experienced in veteran health issues. Wait times were long, but the treatment was worth it. More mental health resources would be beneficial.
